7\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses_in_Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moses_in_Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Okonkwo\", \"score\": 0.9999936719159586, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amy Okonkwo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Okonkwo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Okonkwo\"}, {\"begin\": 407, \"end\": 414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9904078396877752, \"rank\": 0.009683603520882215, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9992454374724279, \"rank\": 0.0007551318794595988, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8816978730060904, \"rank\": 0.13195289893091414, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Notching up that position on day six of the Games will mostly rely on our performance in the pool, as other scheduled events are preliminaries or group stage matches.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In women's basketball, Australia will take on Canada, with the win being almost non-negotiable for Sandy Brondello's team if they want to keep their hopes of staying in Paris beyond the group stage alive and well.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 842, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8816978730060904, \"rank\": 0.13195289893091414, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9932513633240959, \"rank\": 0.005318748460434655, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Brondello\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sandy Brondello\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Brondello\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandy_Brondello\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999736247, \"rank\": 2.6506108905300903e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their unexpected 62-75 loss to Nigeria has thrown a wrench in their plans and now they will need to dig deep to secure a place in the quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1065, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9904078396877752, \"rank\": 0.009683603520882215, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadians are in a similar situation after losing their first game 54-75 to hosts France, and the losers of this match will likely be packing their bags early.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, as one of the two best third-ranked teams, there is a small chance Australia could advance despite a loss.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8816978730060904, \"rank\": 0.13195289893091414, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's and women's field hockey teams, the Kookaburras and the Hockeyroos, have been performing exceptionally well at the Paris Olympics, with only a single loss between them.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1513, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.999999946953723, \"rank\": 5.304612060336776e-08, \"text\": \"Kookaburras\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hockeyroos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Kookaburras, who are coming off a loss to 2020 gold-medallist Belgium, will want to get the better of New Zealand, who are coming fourth in their pool.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Kookaburras\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1713, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9978662741025416, \"rank\": 0.001714914010057076, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1753, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8111708178113752, \"rank\": 0.16758808855456273, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the so-far-undefeated Hockeyroos will face a tough challenge, going head-to-head with Argentina, who finished second at the previous Olympic Games in Tokyo and currently share the top pool spot with Australia.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hockeyroos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1901, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9941422077789357, \"rank\": 0.003941857965909662, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_men's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_men's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999108028657139, \"rank\": 8.920509098468407e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8816978730060904, \"rank\": 0.13195289893091414, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ten of the 16 medals Australia have won so far at the Paris Games have come from the swim team.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2047, \"end\": 2056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.8816978730060904, \"rank\": 0.13195289893091414, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will want to keep that momentum going once again early on Friday.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Abbey Lee Connor and Liz Dekkers will be hoping for a good spot in the women's 200m butterfly final.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abbey_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abbey Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abbey_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abbey_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2205, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connor_MacLeod\", \"score\": 0.9999337412001844, \"rank\": 6.612594580006313e-05, \"text\": \"Connor\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connor_MacLeod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connor_MacLeod\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the women's 200m backstroke heats, Kaylee McKeown and Jaclyn Barclay will compete for a place in the final.\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2335, \"end\": 2349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylee McKeown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the men's 50m freestyle heats, Ben Armbruster and Cameron McEvoy will size up their chances for a spot in the semis.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2462, \"end\": 2476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_McEvoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cameron McEvoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_McEvoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameron_McEvoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian 3x3 basketball team will play two games for their pool